txt.en: Akvosh can be found at the West-delf in the Wildwood.\n\nYou should summon and confront Akvosh.
You have defeated Akvosh and assisted the Free Peoples of the Wildwood.
A bounty notice asks you to seek out Akvosh, a devious Orc in Wildwood.
'Well then, have ya come to hunt the hunter? You can try, ya puny [placeholder]!'

The bounty notice reads:

'Who among you wishes to walk through the Wildwood without fear by your side? It is not possible when a rusty Tarkrîp dagger could be plunged into your back at any moment!

'Of all the Tarkrîp Orcs, there is one that stalks the woods, killing any who wander alone. Akvosh is his name. A reward to any who can bring the vile Orc down.'
